 <text>
  <front>
   <head>THE WAEFU' HEART.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="octet">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">GIN living worth could win my heart,</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">You would na speak in vain;</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">But in the darksome grave it's laid,</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Never to rise again.</l>
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">My waefu' heart lies low wi' his,</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Whose heart was only mine;</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">And, O! what a heart was that to lose, —</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">But I maun no repine.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2" stanza_type="octet">
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Yet, O! gin heaven in mercy soon</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Would grant the boon I crave,</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">And take this life, now naething worth,</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Since Jamie's in his grave.</l>
     <l n="13" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">And see! his gentle spirit comes</l>
     <l n="14" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">To show me on my way;</l>
     <l n="15" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Surpris'd, nae doubt, I still am here, —</l>
     <l n="16" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Sair wondering at my stay.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="3" stanza_type="octet">
     <l n="17" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">I come, I come, my Jamie dear;</l>
     <l n="18" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">And O! wi' what good will</l>
     <l n="19" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">I follow wheresoe'er ye lead!</l>
     <l n="20" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Ye canna lead to ill.</l>
     <l n="21" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">She said; and soon a deadly pale</l>
     <l n="22" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Her faded cheek possess'd;</l>
     <l n="23" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Her waefu' heart forgot to beat, —</l>
     <l n="24" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Her sorrows sunk to rest.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
